E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20rent%20payments%20don't%20count%20in%20your%20credit%20score%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fcredit-score-basics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECredit%20scores%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20calculated%20based%20on%20a%20variety%20of%20factors%20using%20information%20that's%20reported%20to%20credit%20bureaus.%20Payment%20history%20weighs%20heavily%20on%20a%20credit%20score%2C%20but%20historically%2C%20credit%20bureaus%20have%20only%20collected%20information%20on%20payments%20toward%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-credit-cards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecredit%20cards%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20loans%2C%20and%20some%20unpaid%20bills.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECreditors%20and%20lenders%20use%20your%20credit%20history%20to%20determine%20whether%20you'll%20make%20a%20good%20customer%20%E2%80%94%20not%20only%20because%20you%20repay%20debt%20on%20time%20but%20also%20because%20you%20use%20debt%20products%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20On-time%20payments%20toward%20rent%20and%20bills%20have%20been%20ignored%20by%20credit%20scoring%20models%20in%20part%20because%20they%20don't%20give%20creditors%20any%20indication%20that%20you'll%20be%20a%20lucrative%20customer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20oversight%20creates%20a%20barrier%20for%20many%20people%20to%20build%20credit.%20You%20can%20earn%20plenty%20of%20money%20and%20pay%20your%20bills%20on%20time%2C%20but%20if%20you%20don't%20use%20debt%20products%2C%20you%20might%20not%20have%20a%20good%20credit%20score%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20good%20credit%20score%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20access%20to%20debt%20products.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFolks%20who%20benefit%20from%20generational%20wealth%20or%20privilege%20might%20be%20able%20to%20build%20a%20credit%20score%20by%20piggybacking%20off%20of%20a%20family%20member's%20access%20to%20credit%20as%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fadd-child-authorized-user-credit-card%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eauthorized%20user%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Those%20with%20disposable%20income%20might%20be%20able%20to%20build%20credit%20through%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fwhat-is-a-secured-credit-card%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esecured%20credit%20cards%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20loans.%20But%20many%20people%20starting%20from%20zero%20remain%20in%20a%20cycle%20of%20bad%20credit%20and%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20resources%20because%20they're%20not%20able%20to%20participate%20in%20our%20financial%20systems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20good%20credit%20score%20is%20essential%20for%20many%20things%20in%20life%2C%20such%20as%20buying%20a%20car%2C%20applying%20for%20a%20job%2C%20or%20eventually%20purchasing%20a%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kristian%20Lund%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20rent%20and%20bills%20reporting%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Flevelcredit-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESelf%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20credit-building%20platform%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20economic%20inclusion.%3Cspan%3E%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20'get%20credit'%20for%20the%20rent%20payments%20you're%20already%20making%20to%20improve%20your%20credit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220971c131-204d-4cd6-aaaa-8d37ca1d50f6%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20difference%20rent%20reporting%20can%20make%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENewer%20models%20of%20both%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fwhat-is-fico-score%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFICO%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fwhat-is-vantagescore%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVantageScore%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20factor%20reported%20rent%20payments%20into%20your%20payment%20history%2C%20but%20they%20can%20only%20consider%20information%20that's%20reported%20to%20credit%20bureaus.%20Property%20owners%20and%20managers%20don't%20usually%20report%20rent%20payments%20automatically%2C%20so%20you%20have%20to%20use%20an%20intermediary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20companies%20have%20stepped%20in%20to%20fill%20this%20gap.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fbest-rent-reporting-services%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERent%20reporting%20services%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20including%20Self%2C%20Boom%2C%20Rental%20Kharma%2C%20and%20more%2C%20can%20pass%20your%20rent%20payment%20information%20onto%20credit%20bureaus.%20Some%20services%20work%20with%20landlords%20to%20report%20rent%20payments%20automatically%2C%20and%20some%20require%20you%20to%20sign%20up%20as%20a%20tenant.%20Check%20with%20your%20landlord%20or%20property%20manager%20to%20see%20what's%20available%20where%20you%20rent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20amount%20of%20rent%20paid%20has%20little%20to%20no%20impact%20on%20the%20credit%20score%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kristy%20Kim%2C%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20TomoCredit%2C%20a%20credit%20card%20that%20helps%20underserved%20communities%20build%20credit.%20%26quot%3BThis%20means%20that%20people%20with%20more%20affordable%20housing%20still%20benefit%20equally%20from%20demonstrating%20their%20reliability%20in%20paying%20rent%2C%20making%20it%20an%20accessible%20and%20inclusive%20way%20to%20build%20credit%20for%20all%20income%20levels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELund%20notes%20rent%20payments%20can%20impact%20four%20factors%20FICO%20and%20VantageScore%20use%20to%20calculate%20a%20credit%20score%3A%20payment%20history%2C%20average%20age%20of%20credit%2C%20credit%20mix%2C%20and%20new%20credit%2C%20with%20payment%20history%20being%20the%20most%20important.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BMany%20consumers%2C%20especially%20those%20with%20no%20or%20low%20credit%2C%20don't%20have%20enough%20credit%20depth%20and%20history%20for%20the%20scoring%20models%20and%20lenders%20to%20accurately%20predict%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lund.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20where%20additional%2C%20non-debt%20based%20data%20can%20really%20make%20an%20impact%20on%20a%20consumer's%20credit%20history%20and%20credit%20score.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20the%20impact%20can%20be%20significant%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.transunion.com%2Ftransunion-report-finds-37-increase-in-number-of-property-managers-reporting-rent-payments-since-last-year%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ETransUnion%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%2080%25%20of%20renters%20whose%20payments%20were%20reported%20to%20credit%20bureaus%20saw%20an%20increase%20in%20their%20credit%20scores.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BFor%20people%20who%20may%20be%20experiencing%20financial%20hurdles%2C%20rent%20reporting%20can%20be%20beneficial%2C%20because%20it%20enables%20them%20to%20build%20credit%20without%20taking%20on%20additional%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lund.%20Reporting%20rent%2C%20%26quot%3Bshows%20lenders%20that%20consumers%20have%20responsibly%20made%20continuous%20on-time%20payments%20for%20what%20is%20likely%20their%20largest%20expense%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3