20data%20from%20Bank%20of%20America.%20The%20theory%20goes%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20stock%20market%20sees%20a%20compelling%20dip%2C%20investors%20will%20rush%20in%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-outlook-chart-of-the-day-year-end-rally-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeploying%20their%20cash%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20preventing%20any%20downturn%20from%20spiraling%20out%20of%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20gained%20steam%20in%20September%20when%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20started%20cutting%20interest%20rates%2C%20which%20made%20holding%20cash%20slightly%20less%20attractive.%20The%20hope%20was%20that%20as%20yields%20on%20safer%20assets%20came%20down%2C%20investors%20would%20flock%20back%20to%20the%20stock%20market%20and%20spur%20a%20fresh%20run%20of%20gains.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20bulls%20are%20counting%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-money-wall-drive-stocks-july-record-highs-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20%26quot%3Bwall%20of%20money%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20rescue%20the%20stock%20market%20during%20its%20next%20big%20sell-off%2C%20they%20might%20adjust%20their%20thinking.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20why.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d721a21d-48ca-4702-8b2b-3a6733a38fbb%5C%22%3EIt's%20cash%20optimization%2C%20not%20risk%20reduction%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20this%20bif%20the%20bull%20thesis%20is%20that%20much%20of%20the%20increase%20in%20assets%20in%20money%20market%20funds%20is%20being%20driven%20by%20cash%20optimization%20decisions%20among%20investors%2C%20according%20to%20Jay%20Hatfield%2C%20CEO%20of%20Infrastructure%20Capital%20Advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20period%20of%20rising%20money%20market%20assets%2C%20the%20level%20of%20M1%2C%20which%20included%20checking%20accounts%20but%20not%20money%20market%20assets%2C%20declined%20by%20over%20%242%20trillion%2C%20indicating%20that%20the%20increase%20in%20money%20market%20balances%20was%20mostly%20optimization%20activity%20and%20not%20risk%20reduction%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20Hatfield%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20investors%20took%20advantage%20of%205%25%20cash%20yields%20by%20transferring%20their%20money%20out%20of%20low-yielding%20bank%20checking%20accounts%20and%20transferring%20it%20into%20money%20market%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20long%20as%20cash%20yields%20don't%20crash%20to%20zero%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20that%20cash%20on%20the%20sidelines%20will%20seek%20other%20investment%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20if%20yields%20did%20tumble%20to%200%25%2C%20that%20probably%20means%20the%20economy%20is%20in%20trouble%2C%20in%20which%20case%20investors%20will%20probably%20not%20be%20eager%20to%20move%20their%20risk-free%20cash%20into%20a%20more%20volatile%20asset%20like%20stocks.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226664664e-a014-43c1-a343-1375b9d3fe94%5C%22%3E%247%20trillion%20ain't%20what%20it%20used%20to%20be%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Larry%20Tentarelli%2C%20chief%20technical%20strategist%20at%20the%20Blue%20Chip%20Daily%20Trend%20Report%2C%20the%20record%20%247%20trillion%20in%20cash%20isn't%20all%20that%20impressive%20an%20amount%2C%20at%20least%20on%20a%20relative%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20data%20analysis%20by%20Tentarelli%20showed%20that%20money%20market%20cash%20has%20been%20steadily%20declining%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20total%20market%20capitalization%20even%20as%20the%20absolute%20number%20has%20hit%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20point%20is%20ultimately%20noise%20for%20Tentarelli%2C%20who%20thinks%20it%20should%20be%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20that%20we%20should%20expect%20a%20sudden%20influx%20of%20cash%20into%20the%20equity%20markets%20from%20money%20market%20funds%20or%20that%20this%20'dry%20powder'%20should%20be%20considered%20as%20either%20bullish%20(money%20ready%20to%20come%20in)%20or%20bearish%20(investors%20scared%20to%20commit)%2C%26quot%3B%20Tentarelli%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e08be2b1-6a3e-4c27-8c35-b9f5a4fdcb56%5C%22%3EStrategic%20cash%20reserves%20do%20exist%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20some%20investors%20sitting%20on%20cash%20are%20waiting%20to%20pounce%20on%20any%20significant%20stock%20market%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20Hunt%2C%20a%20retail%20investor%20from%20Kentucky%2C%20told%20BI%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretail-investors-stock-market-bullish-sentiment-trump-trade-hood-pltr-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20viewed%20the%20stock%20market%20as%20ripe%20for%20a%20correction%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20believed%20investors%20were%20exhibiting%20signs%20of%20exuberance.%20This%20key%20behavior%20has%20historically%20occurred%20right%20before%20a%20market%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20plan%20to%20raise%20up%20to%2050%25%20cash%20in%20my%20portfolio%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20quarter%2C%26quot%3B%20Hunt%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20already%20at%2030%25%20cash%20in%20his%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHunt%20said%20he%20would%20use%20that%20cash%20to%20strategically%20buy%20a%20bigger%20decline%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20%26quot%3Bhopefully%20at%20lower%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20dip%20buyers%20don't%20seem%20to%20see%20any%20bargains%20just%20yet%20as%20the%20stock%20market%20declines%20on%20worries%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-dow-worst-day-economic-data-consumer-sentiment-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efading%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%