20in%202019.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup%20said%20it%20raised%20%24100M%20in%20a%20Series%20C%20funding%20round%20in%202024%20at%20a%20%241.8B%20valuation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20shared%20how%20he%20pitched%20his%20climate-change-focused%20startup%20to%20investors%20during%20Trump's%20first%20term.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20cofounder%20of%20Watershed%2C%20an%20emissions%20data-tracking%20startup%2C%20Taylor%20Francis's%20job%20is%20to%20convince%20companies%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20reducing%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20%E2%80%94%20even%20in%20a%20political%20landscape%20that%20may%20be%20hostile%20to%20climate%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrancis%20co-founded%20the%20software%20startup%20in%202019%20with%20two%20former%20Stripe%20colleagues%2C%20Avi%20Itskovich%20and%20Christian%20Anderson%2C%20at%20the%20tail%20end%20of%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration%2C%20which%20aggressively%20scaled%20back%20climate-oriented%20incentives%20and%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20their%20investor%20pitch%20was%20simple%3A%20There's%20money%20to%20be%20made%20in%20climate%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20years%20later%2C%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20a%20second%20Trump%20term%2C%20Francis%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20message%20remains%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20here%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202024%2C%20the%20startup%20announced%20a%20%24100%20million%20Series%20C%20funding%20round%20at%20a%20%241.8%20billion%20valuation.%20And%20January%202025%20was%20Watershed's%20%26quot%3Bbest%20month%20ever%20as%20a%20business%26quot%3B%20regarding%20new%20revenue%2C%20Francis%20said.%20He%20did%20not%20disclose%20a%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Francis%20said%20his%20biggest%20competitors%20are%20Salesforce%20and%20Microsoft%20which%20also%20offer%20similar%20emissions-tracking%20services.%20He%20said%20his%20clients%20include%2060%20of%20the%20Fortune%20500%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20that's%20a%20problem%20we've%20earned%20our%20way%20into%20recently%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20visited%20Francis%20at%20Watershed's%2023%2C000-square-foot%20office%20in%20San%20Francisco's%20SoMa%20neighborhood%2C%20where%20his%20nearly%20400%20employees%20are%20encouraged%20to%20come%20into%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20BI%20he%20likes%20to%20operate%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Bold%20school%26quot%3B%20way%3A%20in%20person%2C%20where%20people%20can%20freely%20exchange%20ideas%20in%20front%20of%20a%20whiteboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrancis%20shared%20how%20he%20first%20pitched%20his%20company%20to%20investors%20in%202019%20and%20the%20challenges%20he%20navigates%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20interview%20was%20condensed%20and%20edited%20for%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20it%20hard%20getting%20companies%20onboard%20with%20Watershed%20in%202019%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20I%20mean%2C%202019%20was%20in%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seemed%20no%20one%20had%20ever%20done%20this%20before%20%E2%80%94%20getting%20companies%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20software%20for%20climate.%20People%20had%20spent%20money%20on%20consultants%2C%20they'd%20spent%20money%20on%20%5Bcarbon%5D%20offsets.%20And%20I%20think%20that%20the%20mega%20trend%20that%20we%20are%20both%20riding%20and%20trying%20to%20accelerate%20is%20that%20climate%20is%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20in-the-money%20for%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%20was%20the%20pitch%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20money%20in%20pursuing%20climate%20initiatives.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20the%20first%20slide%20of%20our%20sales%20deck%20was%20the%20same%20in%202019%20as%20it%20is%20today.%20Literally%20the%20first%20slide%20of%20the%20sales%20deck.%20It%20looks%20better%2C%20it's%20been%20redesigned%2C%20but%20it%20still%20says%3A%20%26quot%3BSoftware%20to%20measure%2C%20reduce%2C%20and%20report%20your%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20because%20climate%20action%20is%20good%20for%20your%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20thing%2C%20I'll%20say%20January%202025%20was%20our%20best%20month%20ever%20as%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20you%20think%20is%20happening%20there%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20we%20are%20indexed%20to%20companies%20doing%20the%20work%20on%20climate%2C%20not%20indexed%20to%20companies%20talking%20publicly%20about%20their%20work%20on%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20see%20now%20that%20companies%20are%20behind%20the%20scenes.%20When%20you're%20an%20enterprise%20software%2C%20you%20kind%20of%20get%20to%20see%20the%20inside%20of%20organizations%20and%20whether%20they're%20thinking%20about%20this%20in%20a%20thoughtful%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20are%20going%20about%20this%20with%20more%20organizational%20seriousness%20now%20than%20they%20did%20three%20years%20ago.%20They're%20saying%20much%20less%20about%20it%2C%20but%20the%20executive%20leader%20who's%20responsible%20has%20shifted%20from%20chief%20sustainability%20officer%20to%20the%20chief%20financial%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Watershed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c1319f69253ccddf97de78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWatershed%20office%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20California.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20are%20your%20competitors%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20and%20Salesforce.%20They%20have%20these%20modules.%20It's%20nice%20market%20validation%20that%20they%20think%20this%20is%20a%20big%20opportunity%2C%20but%20there's%20just%20a%20difference%20in%20product%20quality%20when%20it's%20the%20only%20thing%20you%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20Salesforce%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email%20that%20sustainability%20management%20is%20%26quot%3Bfundamentally%20a%20data%20challenge%26quot%3B%20that%20requires%20a%20unified%20platform.%20A%20Microsoft%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20hardest%20thing%20right%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20pretty%20pedestrian%3A%20enterprise%20software%20challenges.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHow%20do%20you%20make%20it%20a%20no-brainer%20for%20companies%20to%20buy%20a%20nice%20piece%20of%20software%20rather%20than%20a%20module%20from%20someone%20they've%20already%20purchased%20from%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20manage%20a%20growing%20team%20between%20San%20Francisco%20and%20London%3F%20Two%20years%20ago%2C%20Watershed%20was%20a%20hundred%20people%2C%20now%20it's%20380%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20make%20sure%20you're%20delivering%20well%20for%20companies%20at%20the%20scale%20of%20Walmart%20who%20have%20enormous%20expectations%20about%20this%20sort%20of%20thing%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20many%20customers%20do%20you%20have%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20know%20that%20we've%20shared%20that%20publicly%2C%20but%20we%20have%20more%20than%20500%20clients%20now%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethan%20the%205%20clients%20we%20had%20when%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmike-moritz-john-doerr-invest-watershed-first-since-google-1999-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJohn%20Doerr%3C%2Fa%3E%20%5Bthe%20Chair%20of%20Kleiner%20Perkins%5D%20joined%20us%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20your%20reaction%20when%20BlackRock%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Watershed%20client%20with%20%2411.6%20trillion%20in%20assets%20under%20management%20%E2%80%94%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20Net%20Zero%20Asset%20Management%20Initiative%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20work%20with%20a%20pretty%20broad%20set%20of%20the%20financial%20sector%20and%20I%20will%20say%20that%20they%20are%20doing%20the%20work%20with%20more%20seriousness%20today%20than%20when%20we%20started%20working%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20I%20think%20there%20just%20is%20this%20talk-action%20ratio%20thing%2C%20where%20a%20bunch%20of%20companies%20around%20the%20Glasgow%20climate%20conference%20came%20out%20with%20huge%20press%20releases%20with%20big%20bold%20claims%20and%20had%20not%20really%20figured%20out%20the%20data%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20you%20see%20the%20pullback%20on%20the%20pledges%2C%20and%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20behind%20the%20scenes%20%E2%80%94%20know%20what%20they're%20doing.%20They've%20got%20the%20initiatives%20that%20they're%20prioritizing.%20So%20I%20think%20the%20talk-action%20ratio%20has%20flipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20a%20good%20time%20for%20climate%20action%20in%20the%20world%20right%20now%3F%20No.%20Obviously%20the%20policy%20pendulum%20matters%20and%20the%20policy%20pendulum%20is%20not%20swinging%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%20But%20%E2%80%94%20behind%20the%20scenes%20with%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20people%20are%20doing%20more%2C%20even%20though%20they're%20talking%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwatershed-taylor-francis-how-to-pitch-startup-salesforce-microsoft-compeitition-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740833702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c1f9d9b1834fe31165cfb6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwatershed-taylor-francis-how-to-pitch-startup-salesforce-microsoft-compeitition-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Watershed%20co-founder%20Taylor%20Francis%20started%20his%20emissions-data%20startup%20in%202019%20and%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bearned%26quot%3B%20his%20way%20to%20compete%20with%20Microsoft%20a