dent%20Zelensky%20is%20not%20ready%20for%20Peace%20if%20America%20is%20involved%2C%20because%20he%20feels%20our%20involvement%20gives%20him%20a%20big%20advantage%20in%20negotiations.%20He%20disrespected%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%20in%20its%20cherished%20Oval%20Office.%20He%20can%20come%20back%20when%20he%20is%20ready%20for%20Peace%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Trump%20posted%20on%20Truth%20Social.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Zelensky%20thanked%20dozens%20of%20allies%20on%20social%20media%20on%20Saturday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Mr%20Trump%20and%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20accused%20him%20of%20not%20being%20sufficiently%20grateful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20on%20X%20wrote%20the%20words%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%20for%20your%20support%26quot%3B%20in%20individual%20replies%20to%20around%2030%20messages%20of%20support%20from%20European%20leaders%20after%20his%20much%20publicised%20clash%20with%20the%20new%20US%20administration%20in%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20confrontation%2C%20Zelensky%20earlier%20thanked%20Mr%20Trump%2C%20the%20US%20Congress%20and%20the%20American%20people%20for%20their%20support%20and%20for%20his%20visit.%20Today%20again%2C%20he%20reiterated%20that%20in%20a%20separate%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20very%20grateful%20to%20the%20United%20States%20for%20all%20the%20support.%20I'm%20thankful%20to%20President%20Trump%2C%20Congress%20for%20their%20bipartisan%20support%2C%20and%20American%20people.%20Ukrainians%20have%20always%20appreciated%20this%20support%2C%20especially%20during%20these%20three%20years%20of%20full-scale%20invasion.%20America's%20help%20has%20been%20vital%20in%20helping%20us%20survive%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20acknowledge%20that.%20Despite%20the%20tough%20dialogue%2C%20we%20remain%20strategic%20partners.%20But%20we%20need%20to%20be%20honest%20and%20direct%20with%20each%20other%20to%20truly%20understand%20our%20shared%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Zelensky%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20crucial%20for%20us%20to%20have%20President%20Trump's%20support.%20He%20wants%20to%20end%20the%20war%2C%20but%20no%20one%20wants%20peace%20more%20than%20we%20do.%20We%20are%20the%20ones%20living%20this%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20It's%20a%20fight%20for%20our%20freedom%2C%20for%20our%20very%20survival%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Zelensky%2C%20quoting%20President%20Ronald%20Reagan's%20%26quot%3BPeace%20is%20not%20just%20the%20absence%20of%20war%26quot%3B%2C%20stressed%20that%20Ukraine%20is%20talking%20about%20just%20and%20lasting%20peace.%20He%20further%20said%20that%20a%20ceasefire%20won't%20work%20with%20Putin%2C%20as%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bbroken%20ceasefires%2025%20times%20over%20the%20last%20ten%20years%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20first%20step%20towards%20peace%2C%20Mr%20Zelensky%2C%20despite%20the%20bitter%20Oval%20Office%20memory%2C%20said%20he%20is%20ready%20to%20sign%20the%20minerals%20deal%20and%20that%20Ukrainian%20people%20%26quot%3Bneed%20to%20know%20that%20America%20is%20on%20our%20side%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20ready%20to%20sign%20the%20minerals%20agreement%2C%20and%20it%20will%20be%20the%20first%20step%20toward%20security%20guarantees.%20But%20it's%20not%20enough%2C%20and%20we%20need%20more%20than%20just%20that.%20A%20ceasefire%20without%20security%20guarantees%20is%20dangerous%20for%20Ukraine.%20We've%20been%20fighting%20for%203%20years%2C%20and%20Ukrainian%20people%20need%20to%20know%20that%20America%20is%20on%20our%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Zelensky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Zelensky%20maintained%20that%20%26quot%3BRussia%20is%20the%20enemy%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20Ukraine%20needs%20to%20be%20strong%20at%20the%20negotiation%20table.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20change%20Ukraine's%20position%20on%20Russia.%20The%20Russians%20are%20killing%20us.%20Russia%20is%20the%20enemy%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20reality%20we%20face.%20Ukraine%20wants%20peace%2C%20but%20it%20must%20be%20a%20just%20and%20lasting%20peace.%20For%20that%2C%20we%20need%20to%20be%20strong%20at%20the%20negotiation%20table.%20Peace%20can%20only%20come%20when%20we%20know%20we%20have%20security%20guarantees%2C%20when%20our%20army%20is%20strong%2C%20and%20our%20partners%20are%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740832740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F8qgfev_zelensky-_625x300_01_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fukraine-wants-real-peace-ready-to-sign-minerals-deal-says-zelensky-hours-after-oval-office-clash-with-trump-7823537%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20shouting%20match%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%2C%20broadcast%20worldwide%2C%20with%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20appears%20to%20have%20not%20deterred%20Ukraine%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fans%20say%2C%20'hope%20it's%20not%20silly%20ad'%20as%20makers%20tease%20ZNMD%20sequel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740832212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118649539%2Cimgsize-40152.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffans-say-hope-its-not-another-silly-ad-as-hrithik-roshan-farhan-akhtar-abhay-deol-tease-the-internet-with-new-pic-seeming-like-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara-sequel%2Farticleshow%2F118649542.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118649542.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHrithik%20Roshan%2C%20Farhan%20Akhtar%2C