20are%20just%20some%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bdating%20pains%26quot%3B%20the%20two%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20began%20building%20Left%20Field%20in%202024%20and%20have%20since%20quit%20their%20jobs%20in%20finance%20and%20consulting%20after%20raising%20a%20family%20and%20friends%20funding%20round.%20Sean%20Miller%2C%20a%20founding%20engineer%20at%20fintech%20startup%20Apollo%20Card%2C%20joined%20Left%20Field%20as%20its%20technical%20cofounder%20in%202025.%20The%20app%20officially%20launched%20on%20the%20Apple%20App%20Store%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20how%20Left%20Field%20works%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20profile%20itself%20is%20similar%20to%20many%20dating%20apps%20(it%20has%20photos%2C%20biographical%20details%2C%20and%20some%20prompts).%20However%2C%20instead%20of%20swiping%20through%20a%20stack%20of%20nearby%20singles%2C%20the%20app%20will%20send%20push%20notifications%20of%20a%20potential%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-apps-look-to-matchmaking-over-swiping-startups-tinder-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematch%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20area%20if%20location%20services%20are%20enabled%20and%20a%20user%20crosses%20paths%20with%20someone%20on%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20like%20to%20call%20ourselves%20the%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20Go%20of%20dating%2C%26quot%3B%20Martin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20is%20that%20Left%20Field%20is%20a%20more%20passive%20way%20to%20date%2C%20where%20you%20can%20toggle%20location%20services%20on%20and%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20interested%20in%20meeting%20someone%2C%20you%20just%20turn%20on%20the%20app%2C%20and%20then%20you%20can%20close%20it%20and%20forget%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Sieler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20dating%20app%20to%20try%20to%20capture%20the%20feeling%20of%20crossing%20paths%20with%20someone%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHappn%2C%20a%20French%20dating%20app%2C%20launched%20a%20decade%20ago%