ophone%20in%20front%20of%20his%20face%2C%20and%20is%20wearing%20black%20glasses%2C%20a%20navy%20suit%2C%20and%20a%20pale%20blue%20shirt.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c21a28b8b41a9673f95bf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDario%20Amodei%20believes%20it's%20possible%20to%20address%20the%20risks%20of%20AI%20without%20foregoing%20the%20solutions%20it%20affords.%3Cp%3EFABRICE%20COFFRINI%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20said%20that%20while%20the%20benefits%20of%20AI%20are%20big%2C%20so%20are%20the%20risks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmodei%20said%20on%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F02%2F28%2Fpodcasts%2Fhardfork-anthropic-dario-amodei.html%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHard%20Fork%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20worries%20about%20threats%20to%20national%20security%20and%20the%20misuse%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20believes%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20address%20the%20risks%20of%20AI%20without%20foregoing%20the%20solutions%20it%20affords.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20said%20that%20people%20still%20aren't%20taking%20AI%20seriously%20enough%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20expects%20that%20to%20change%20within%20the%20next%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20will%20wake%20up%20to%20both%20the%20risks%20and%20the%20benefits%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Times'%20%26quot%3BHard%20Fork%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20he's%20worried%20the%20realization%20will%20arrive%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bshock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20the%20more%20we%20can%20forewarn%20people%20%E2%80%94%20which%20maybe%20it's%20just%20not%20possible%2C%20but%20I%20want%20to%20try%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20we%20can%20forewarn%20people%2C%20the%20higher%20the%20likelihood%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it's%20still%20very%20low%20%E2%80%94%20of%20a%20sane%20and%20rational%20response.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20optimistic%20about%20the%20technology%20expect%20the%20advent%20of%20powerful%20AI%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20barriers%20to%20niche%20%26quot%3Bknowledge%20work%26quot%3B%20once%20performed%20exclusively%20by%20specialized%20professionals.%20In%20theory%2C%20the%20benefits%20are%20immense%20%E2%80%94%20with%20applications%20that%20could%20help%20solve%20everything%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-ai-be-a-solution-to-the-climate-crisis-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclimate%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20deadly%20disease%20outbreaks.%20But%20the%20corresponding%20risks%2C%20Amodei%20said%2C%20are%20proportionately%20big.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20our%20responsible%20scaling%20policy%2C%20it's%20nothing%20but%20AI%2C%20autonomy%2C%20and%20CBRN%20%E2%80%94%20chemical%2C%20biological%2C%20radiological%2C%20nuclear%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20about%20hardcore%20misuse%20in%20AI%20autonomy%20that%20could%20be%20threats%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20millions%20of%20people.%20That%20is%20what%20Anthropic%20is%20mostly%20worried%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20possibility%20of%20%26quot%3Bmisuse%26quot%3B%20by%20bad%20actors%20could%20arrive%20as%20soon%20as%20%26quot%3B2025%20or%202026%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20he%20doesn't%20know%20when%20exactly%20it%20may%20present%20a%20%26quot%3Breal%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20very%20important%20to%20say%20this%20isn't%20about%2C%20'Oh%2C%20did%20the%20model%20give%20me%20the%20sequence%20for%20this%20thing%3F%20Did%20it%20give%20me%20a%20cookbook%20for%20making%20meth%20or%20something%3F'%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20easy.%20You%20can%20do%20that%20with%20Google.%20We%20don't%20care%20about%20that%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20care%20about%20this%20kind%20of%20esoteric%2C%20high%2C%20uncommon%20knowledge%20that%2C%20say%2C%20only%20a%20virology%20Ph.D.%20or%20something%20has%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20does%20it%20help%20with%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20AI%20can%20act%20as%20a%20substitute%20for%20niche%20higher%20education%2C%20Amodei%20clarifies%2C%20it%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20mean%20we're%20all%20going%20to%20die%20of%20the%20plague%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%20But%20it%20would%20mean%20that%20a%20new%20breed%20of%20danger%20had%20come%20into%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20means%20that%20a%20new%20risk%20exists%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20new%20threat%20vector%20exists%20in%20the%20world%20as%20if%20you%20just%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20build%20a%20nuclear%20weapon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESetting%20aside%20individual%20actors%2C%20Amodei%20expects%20AI%20to%20have%20massive%20implications%20for%20military%20technology%20and%20national%20security.%20In%20particular%2C%20Amodei%20said%20he's%20concerned%20that%20%26quot%3BAI%20could%20be%20an%20engine%20of%20autocracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20think%20about%20repressive%20governments%2C%20the%20limits%20to%20how%20repressive%20they%20can%20be%20are%20generally%20set%20by%20what%20they%20can%20get%20their%20enforcers%2C%20their%20human%20enforcers%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20their%20enforcers%20are%20no%20longer%20human%2C%20that%20starts%20painting%20some%20very%20dark%20possibilities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmodei%20pointed%20to%20Russia%20and%20China%20as%20particular%20areas%20of%20concern%20and%20said%20he%20believes%20it's%20crucial%20for%20the%20US%20to%20remain%20%26quot%3Beven%20with%20China%26quot%3B%20in%20terms%20of%20AI%20development.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20ensure%20that%20%26quot%3Bliberal%20democracies%26quot%3B%20retain%20enough%20%26quot%3Bleverage%20and%20enough%20advantage%20in%20the%20technology%26quot%3B%20to%20check%20abuses%20of%20power%2C%20and%20block%20threats%20to%20national%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20can%20risk%20be%20mitigated%20without%20kneecapping%20benefits%3F%20Beyond%20implementing%20safeguards%20during%20the%20development%20of%20the%20systems%20themselves%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-deepmind-ceo-demis-hassabis-anthropic-ceo-ai-pressure-worries-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eencouraging%20regulatory%20oversight%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Amodei%20doesn't%20have%20any%20magic%20answers%2C%20but%20he%20does%20believe%20it%20can%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20actually%20have%20both.%20There%20are%20ways%20to%20surgically%20and%20carefully%20address%20the%20risks%20without%20slowing%20down%20the%20benefits%20very%20much%2C%20if%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they%20require%20subtlety%2C%20and%20they%20require%20a%20complex%20conversation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20models%20are%20inherently%20%26quot%3Bsomewhat%20difficult%20to%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20said.%20But%20the%20situation%20isn't%20%26quot%3Bhopeless.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20how%20to%20make%20these%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20kind%20of%20a%20plan%20for%20how%20to%20make%20them%20safe%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20a%20plan%20that's%20going%20to%20reliably%20work%20yet.%20Hopefully%2C%20we%20can%20do%20better%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-says-ai-risks-are-being-overlooked-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740827942000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c21ad2b1834fe31165d72b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22