re%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESuccessful%20home%20flippers%20keep%20the%20process%20as%20simple%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20avoid%20unique%20properties%2C%20opting%20for%20standard%20layouts%20to%20attract%20more%20buyers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESuccess%20requires%20understanding%20buyer%20needs%2C%20rather%20than%20thinking%20about%20what%20you%20want%20in%20a%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20done%20correctly%2C%20flipping%20a%20home%20can%20turn%20a%20tidy%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColorado-based%20investor%20Whitney%20Elkins-Hutten%20bought%20her%20first%20property%20%E2%80%94%20a%20single-family%20home%20in%20need%20of%20some%20elbow%20grease%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Fort%20Collins%20in%202002.%20About%20a%20year%20later%2C%20after%20turning%20it%20from%20a%20%26quot%3B1960s%2C%20green%20shag%20carpet%2C%20psychedelic%20daisies%20painted%20all%20over%20the%20walls%20to%20a%20really%20beautiful%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investor-shares-wealth-building-strategies-achieve-financial-independence-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esold%20the%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20walked%20away%20with%20a%20%2452%2C000%20check.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Louisville%2C%20Kentucky%2C%20business%20partners%20Mike%20Gorius%20and%20Kevin%20Hart%20have%20used%20flipping%20to%20get%20%26quot%3Ba%20quick%20capital%20boost%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20told%20BI.%20They%20used%20the%20capital%20boost%20to%20pay%20down%20their%20personal%20debt%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investors-share-their-strategy-flip-and-buy-rentals-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvest%20in%20long-term%20rental%20properties%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigh%20school%20friends%20and%20business%20partners%20Aria%20Khosravi%20and%20Alan%20Blue%20have%20created%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-flip-home-successfully-according-to-real-estate-experts-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20seven-figure%20business%20out%20of%20flipping%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20of%202023%2C%20they%20had%20done%2091%20flips%20in%20the%20Denver%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20commonality%20between%20each%20of%20these%20investors%2C%20who%20do%20business%20in%20different%20regions%20of%20the%20States%2C%20is%20that%20they%20keep%20things%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20so%20simple%20that%20it%20borders%20on%20boring%2C%20suggested%20Hart%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20reality%2C%20if%20you're%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20flips%2C%20flipping%20is%20a%20pretty%20boring%20business.%20You're%20using%20the%20same%20paint%20colors%2C%20you're%20using%20similar%20flooring.%20Whatever's%20in%20style%20that%20year%2C%20we're%20like%2C%20'Okay%2C%20for%20the%20next%20five%20houses%2C%20this%20is%20what%20we're%20doing.'%20We're%20doing%20neutral%20colors%2C%20neutral%20floors%2C%20and%20just%20making%20everything%20fresh%20and%20clean%20so%20that%20it%20appeals%20to%20the%20most%20amount%20of%20people%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20two%20strategies%20each%20of%20these%20successful%20flippers%20have%20used%20to%20simplify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6d9cd86-f732-4481-8bbb-fce67b49e017%5C%22%3E1.%20Stick%20with%20standard%2C%20more%20traditional%20home%20layouts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKhosravi%20and%20Blue%20learned%20to%20avoid%20unique%20properties%20the%20hard%20way.%20On%20their%20second%20flip%2C%20they%20purchased%20%26quot%3Ba%20funky%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20Blue%20said.%20Among%20other%20quirky%20features%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20had%20this%20big%2C%20weird%20detached%20garage%20with%20a%20mother-in-law%20suite%20above%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20ultimately%20lost%20money%20on%20the%20sale.%20Part%20of%20the%20problem%20was%20that%20fewer%20buyers%20were%20interested%20in%20such%20an%20unusual%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20Khosravi%20have%20learned%20that%2C%20generally%2C%20prospective%20buyers%20like%20%26quot%3Bstandard%20layouts%2C%26quot%3B%20such%20as%20a%20two-bed%2C%20two-bath%20with%20a%20kitchen%20and%20a%20dining%20room.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20looking%20at%20a%20house%20that%20feels%20funky%20when%20you%20walk%20in%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20the%20kitchen%20or%20bedrooms%20are%20super%20small%2C%20or%20it%20doesn't%20make%20sense%20where%20they%20are%20in%20the%20layout%20%E2%80%94%20don't%20overlook%20that.%20Because%20if%20you%20feel%20kind%20of%20strange%20when%20you're%20looking%20at%20it%2C%20so%20will%20the%20potential%20buyers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESticking%20with%20a%20more%20standard%20layout%20may%20help%20you%20avoid%20a%20common%20but%20costly%20mistake%3A%20Biting%20off%20more%20than%20you%20can%20chew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20take%20on%20a%20project%20that's%20way%20bigger%20than%20you%20can%20handle%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hart%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20it's%20easier%20said%20than%20done%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20draw%20inspiration%20from%20HGTV%20shows%20that%20tend%20to%20feature%20full%20gut%20renovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20Gorius%20prefer%20buying%203-bed%2C%201-bath%2C%20ranch-style%20homes%20in%20Louisville%20that%20need%20cosmetic%20upgrades%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20new%20flooring%2C%20paint%2C%20and%20light%20fixtures%20%E2%80%94%20rather%20than%20major%20structural%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20want%20to%20start%20a%20huge%20construction%20project%20when%20you%20have%20no%20experience%20doing%20construction%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223cb7f478-3317-4e74-9c95-028ccbb0ec88%5C%22%3E2.%20Don't%20make%20it%20personal.%20Think%20about%20the%20buyer%20and%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20early%20flipping%20mistake%20Elkins-Hutten%20made%20was%20thinking%20about%20what%20she%20would%20want%20to%20see%20in%20a%20home%2C%20rather%20than%20what%20her%20potential%20buyers%20would%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20the%20home%20is%20in%20an%20area%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20families%20are%20moving%20into%20and%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20starter%20home%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20want%20better%20finishes%2C%20they're%20probably%20going%20to%20want%20a%20yard%20with%20a%20fence%2C%20they're%20probably%20going%20to%20want%20good%20soundproofing%20from%20neighbor%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20about%20the%20typical%20buyer%20in%20your%20market%20and%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20they%20want%3F%20I'm%20always%20thinking%20through%2C%20'Who's%20the%20person%20that's%20actually%20going%20to%20use%20this%20property%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221124%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mike%20gorius%20kevin%20hart%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c1ebfab8b41a9673f95212%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22843%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMike%20Gorius%2C%20left%2C%20and%20Kevin%20Hart%20buy%20real%20estate%20in%20Louisville.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Mike%20Gorius%20and%20Kevin%20Hart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGorius%20has%20found%20success%20following%20the%20same%20principle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20pretend%20that%20you're%20the%20one%20moving%20into%20this%20house%20and%20start%20putting%20finishes%20on%20there%20that%20are%20overpriced%20or%20don't%20make%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BStick%20with%20what%20works%2C%20talk%20to%20contractors%2C%20and%20walk%20other%20people's%20flips%20to%20see%20what%20finishes%20and%20paint%20colors%20and%20materials%20they're%20using%2C%20because%20they're%20doing%20that%20for%20a%20reason.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20key%20to%20successful%20flipping%20also%20involves%20reps.%20Khosravi%20and%20Blue%20advise%20going%20into%20your%20first%20flip%20with%20conservative%20projections%20and%20assuming%20that%20everything%20won't%20go%20exactly%20to%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20you've%20come%20across%20every%20situation%20at%20least%20once%2C%20you%20learn%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20those%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Blue.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20mistakes%20along%20the%20way%20and%20they%20cost%20money.%20You%20pay%20for%20your%20education%20one%20way%20or%20the%20other%2C%20and%20we%20opted%20to%20do%20it%20in%20the%20field.%20But%20now%20that%20we've%20been%20doing%20it%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20we%20know%20what%20to%20expect%20and%20we%20know%20what%20to%20look%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-how-to-flip-home-for-profit-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740827702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c1eb9669253ccddf97eaab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-how-to-flip-home-for-profit-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20flipping%20a%20home%2C%20simplicity%20typically%20wins%20out.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-how-to-flip-home-for-profit-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Neena%20doesn't%20want%20Masaba's%20daughter%20to%20call%20her%20'naani'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740827675000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118648584%2Cimgsize-52648.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fneena-gupta-doesnt-want-masaba-guptas-daughter-to-call-her-naani-as-the-actress-has-a-contemporary-approach-to-family-dynamics%2Farticleshow%2F118648584.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesof