ble%20like%20gold%20or%20other%20commodities.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20make%20it%20worthless%3B%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20bitcoin%20has%20several%20clear%20advantages%20over%20other%20cryptos%20and%20even%20traditional%20fiat%20currencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBitcoin's%20supply%20is%20limited%2C%20unlike%20most%20cryptos%20and%20the%20US%20dollar%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20been%20devalued%20by%20inflation%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FM2SL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erampant%20money-printing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20runs%20on%20an%20ultra-secure%2C%20pseudonymous%20network%20where%20there's%20both%20transaction%20transparency%20and%20privacy%20since%20wallets%20aren't%20tied%20to%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20money%20supply%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c2185db1834fe31165d689%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22962%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20US%20money%20supply%20has%20grown%20astronomically%20in%20recent%20decades.%3Cp%3EFederal%20Reserve%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20appreciate%20the%20value%20of%20bitcoin's%20network%2C%20especially%20for%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fafrica.businessinsider.com%2Flocal%2Fmarkets%2Fhow-digital-assets-may-hold-the-key-to-africas-economic-growth%2F992jdxv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithout%20viable%20banking%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20can%20see%20why%20its%20proponents%20see%20it%20as%20a%20crucial%20store%20of%20value%20as%20the%20dollar%20gets%20devalued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20I%20told%20several%20bitcoin%20gurus%2C%20it's%20hard%20for%20me%20to%20buy%20bitcoin%20since%20it%20can't%20be%20valued%20by%20traditional%20metrics.%20Who's%20to%20say%20whether%20it%20should%20sell%20for%20%245%2C000%2C%20%2410%2C000%2C%20or%20%24510%2C000%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20seemed%20to%20mind%20my%20doubts%2C%20and%20one%20attendee%20thanked%20me%20for%20making%20an%20effort%20to%20learn.%20The%20bitcoiners%20agreed%20that%20there's%20no%20reliable%20way%20to%20intrinsically%20value%20the%20asset%2C%20though%20their%20confidence%20isn't%20tied%20to%20a%20mathematical%20formula%20of%20fair%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20bitcoin%20fans'%20bull%20case%20centers%20on%20the%20ECON%20101%20principles%20of%20supply%20and%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBitcoin's%20supply%20is%20capped%20at%2021%20million.%20Close%20to%2020%20million%20units%20are%20already%20in%20circulation%2C%20including%20several%20million%20that%20may%20be%20unrecoverable.%20And%20demand%20is%20steadily%20rising%2C%20including%20from%20asset%20management%20giants%20like%20Fidelity%20and%20BlackRock%2C%20which%20just%20put%20a%20bitcoin%20ETF%20in%20its%20model%20portfolio%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-02-28%2Fblackrock-adds-ibit-to-model-portfolios-that-allow-alternatives%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20the%20first%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Companies%20are%20also%20adding%20bitcoin%20to%20their%20balance%20sheets%2C%20even%20if%20few%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrostrategy-bitcoin-100000-michael-saylor-crypto-markets-investing-strategy-analysis-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoing%20to%20the%20extremes%20of%20MicroStrategy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Crucially%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Ftrump-bitcoin-cryptocurrency-election-outlook-crypto-funding-regulation-biden-novogratz-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenamored%20with%20crypto%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20there's%20even%20been%20talk%20about%20building%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-trump-national-strategic-reserve-debt-inflation-btc-crypto-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrategic