EMaking%20the%20announcement%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Environment%20Minister%20Manjinder%20Singh%20Sirsa%2C%20who%20took%20charge%20on%20Monday%2C%20said%20a%20team%20will%20be%20formed%20to%20identify%20such%20vehicles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20installing%20gadgets%20at%20petrol%20pumps%20which%20will%20identify%20vehicles%20older%20than%2015%20years%20and%20no%20fuel%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sirsa%20said%20after%20holding%20a%20meeting%20with%20officials%20to%20discuss%20steps%20to%20combat%20air%20pollution%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20and%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20have%20a%20policy%20under%20which%20diesel%20vehicles%20older%20than%2010%20years%20and%20petrol%20vehicles%20older%20than%2015%20years%20are%20not%20allowed%20on%20the%20roads.%20An%20order%20in%202021%20had%20also%20said%20that%20such%20vehicles%20would%20be%20impounded%20and%20sent%20to%20the%20scrapyard%20if%20they%20were%20found%20operating%20on%20the%20roads%20after%20January%201%2C%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sirsa%20said%20the%20government's%20initial%20focus%20will%20be%20on%20heavy%20vehicles%20entering%20Delhi%20and%20teams%20will%20check%20whether%20the%20laid-down%20rules%20are%20being%20followed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnti-Smog%20Guns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20there%20are%20several%20big%20organisations%20in%20Delhi%20which%20cause%20pollution%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20they%20will%20be%20instructed%20to%20install%20new%20anti-pollution%20%26quot%3Bgadgets%26quot%3B.%20All%20high-rise%20buildings%2C%20hotels%2C%20and%20commercial%20complexes%20in%20the%20capital%20will%20also%20have%20to%20install%20anti-smog%20guns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20other%20steps%2C%20Mr%20Sirsa%20said%20a%20plantation%20drive%20will%20be%20held%20every%20year%20and%20university%20students%20will%20be%20encouraged%20to%20take%20part%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2