ns%20that%20hard%20work%2C%20rather%20than%20work-life%20balance%2C%20should%20be%20the%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20Business%20Standard%2C%20Mr%20Kant%20said%20it%20had%20become%20%26quot%3Bfashionable%26quot%3B%20to%20talk%20about%20not%20working%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20strongly%20believe%20in%20hard%20work.%20Indians%20must%20work%20hard%2C%20whether%20it's%2080%20hours%20or%2090%20hours%20a%20week.%20If%20your%20ambition%20is%20to%20move%20from%20a%20%244%20trillion%20to%20a%20%2430%20trillion%20economy%2C%20you%20can't%20do%20it%20through%20entertainment%20or%20by%20following%20the%20views%20of%20some%20film%20stars%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kanth%20stated%20that%20people%20must%20work%20hard%20to%20deliver%20projects%20before%20deadlines%20without%20compromising%20on%20quality%20or%20exceeding%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Amitabh%20Kant%2C%20the%20debate%20around%20work-life%20balance%20and%20comments%20saying%20that%20Indians%20should%20not%20work%20too%20hard%20are%20setting%20the%20wrong%20example%20for%20the%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kant's%20comments%20came%20weeks%20after%20L%26amp%3BT%20Chairman%20SN%20Subrahmanyan%20said%20that%20Indians%20%26quot%3Bmust%20be%20willing%20to%20work%2090%20hours%20every%20week%20and%20even%20do%20their%20job%20on%20Sundays%26quot%3B%20to%20enhance%20the%20country's%20competitiveness%20at%20a%20global%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20SN%20Subrahmanyan%2C%20Infosys%20co-founder%20NR%20Narayana%20Murthy%20had%20called%20for%2070-hour%20work%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%2C%20Mr%20Kant%20referenced%20countries%20like%20Korea%20and%20Japan%2C%20who%20he%20said%20achieved%20economic%20success%20due%20to%20a%20strong%20work%20ethic.%20He%20appealed%20to%20the%20audience%20that%20India%20must%20cultivate%20a%20similar%20mindset%20to%20reach%20its%20goal%20of%20becoming%20a%