rjee%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20adding%20fake%20voters%20to%20influence%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20CEO%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20social%20media%2C%20outlining%20the%20procedures%20governing%20electoral%20roll%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20RP%20Act%201950%2C%20Registration%20of%20Electors%20Rules%201960%20and%20Manual%20on%20Electoral%20Rolls%2C%20concerned%20BLOs%2C%20AEROs%2C%20EROs%2C%20DEOs%2C%20and%20CEOs%20in%20any%20State%2FUT%20work%20for%20the%20updation%20of%20Electoral%20Rolls%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThis%20is%20done%20with%20active%20participation%20of%20Booth%20Level%20Agents%20appointed%20by%20political%20parties.%20Any%20specific%20claim%20or%20objections%20are%20to%20be%20made%20first%20before%20the%20concerned%2080%2C633%20BLOs%2C%203%2C049%20AEROs%20and%20294%20EROs%20in%20West%20Bengal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20from%20the%20election%20authority%20came%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20announcement%20of%20a%20committee%20to%20scrutinise%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20voter%20lists%20across%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPolitical%20parties%20are%20involved%20in%20every%20step%20of%20making%20the%20voter%20list.%20If%20there%20is%20any%20objection%20from%20any%20political%20parties%20on%20any%20step%2C%20it%20is%20heard%20immediately.%20Every%20objection%20to%20adding%20or%20deleting%20names%20is%20investigated%20by%20the%20electoral%20roll%20officer%2C%26quot%3B%20election%20commission%20sources%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20raised%20questions%20about%20adding%2048%20lakh%20voters%20in%20Maharashtra%20after%20the%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%20But%20only%20one%20complaint%20made%20it%20to%20the%20CEO's%20office.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20manipulating%20voter%20lists%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20alleged%20electoral%20malpractices%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Delhi.%20She%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20employed%20similar%20tactics%20in%20other%20states%20and%20was%20now%20attempting%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSitting%20in%20the%20Election%20Commissioner's%20office%2C%20they%20have%20created%20a%20fake%20voter's%20list%20online%2C%20and%20in%20every%20district%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20fake%20voters%20have%20been%20added%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said.%20%26quot%3BUsing%20this%20trick%2C%20they%20have%20won%20elections%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Maharashtra.%20The%20opposition%20in%20Maharashtra%20could%20not%20find%20out%20these%20facts.%20Most%20of%20the%20fake%20voters%20are%20from%20Haryana%20and%20Gujarat.%20BJP%20is%20manipulating%20voters%20list%20with%20the%20blessing%20of%20EC%2C%20Bengal's%20culture%20gave%20rise%20to%20independence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20urged%20the%20people%20of%20West%20Bengal%20to%20verify%20their%20names%20on%20the%20voter%20list%2C%20warning%20that%20legitimate%20voters%20could%20be%20removed%20under%20the%20pretext%20of%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20and%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20actual%20names%20can%20be%20removed%20any%20day%20in%20the%20name%20of%20NRC%20and%20CAA.%20It%20has%20two%20main%20objectives.%20One%20is%20to%20defeat%20TMC%20and%20to%20remove%20the%20names%20of%20persons%20on%20the%20list.%20This%20is%20being%20done%20with%20the%20blessings%20of%20the%20EC.%20Keep%20a%20watch%20on%20data%20operators.%20If%20anyone%20is%20at%20the%20grassroots%2C%20then%20it%20is%20TMC.%20In%20the%202026%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20we%20have%20to%20hit%20the%20ball%20harder%2C%20and%20this%20would%20start%20from%20the%20voter's%20list.%20This%20has%20to%20be%20done%20at%20the%20booth%20level.%20District%20president%20would%20have%20to%20take%20care%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20counter%20the%20alleged%20voter%20list%20manipulation%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20announced%20the%20formation%20of%20an%20IT%20Media%20cell%2C%20panchayat%20councillors%2C%20and%20a%20core%20committee%20to%20monitor%20the%20electoral%20rolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20concerns%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20leaders%20initiated%20a%20door-to-door%20campaign%20to%20scrutinise%20the%20electoral%20rolls.%20The%20campaign%2C%20which%20began%20today%2C%20aims%20to%20identify%20any%20discrepancies%20in%20the%20voter%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Mayor%20Firhad%20Hakim%20personally%20participated%20in%20the%20verification%20drive%20in%20South%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20manipulate%20the%20electoral%20rolls%20by%20bringing%20in%20fake%20voters%20from%20other%20states.%20So%2C%20along%20with%20our%20party%20workers%2C%20we%20are%20on%20a%20door-to-door%20visit%20to%20verify%20the%20voter%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hakim%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20verification%20efforts%20were%20underway%20in%20Bhabanipur%2C%20the%20assembly%20constituency%20of%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20with%20local%20TMC%20leaders%20actively%20participating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETMC%20leaders%20claimed%20that%20multiple%20individuals%20from%20outside%20West%20Bengal%20had%20been%20registered%20under%20the%20same%20Electoral%20Photo%20Identity%20Card%20(EPIC)%20number%20as%20genuine%20voters%20in%20the%20state.%20Ms%20Banerjee%20labeled%20these%20fraudulent%20entries%20as%20%26quot%3Bghost%20voters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740823380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fvok7s2io_mamata-banerjee_625x300_27_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-mamata-banerjees-election-manipulation-claim-a-poll-body-reply-7822927%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22West%20Bengal's%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%20(CEO)%20has%20dismissed%20Chief%