%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fsnoop-doggs-daughter-cori-broadus-welcomes-baby-girl-prematurely-at-25-weeks%2Farticleshow%2F118643106.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20What%20Really%20Are%20Shashi%20Tharoor's%20'Options'%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20is%20quite%20the%20darling%20of%20the%20middle%20classes.%20He%20is%20charming%2C%20well%20spoken%2C%20erudite%2C%20a%20skilled%20debator%20and%20has%20a%20felicity%20with%20the%20English%20language%20that%20he%20uses%20to%20great%20effect%20by%20throwing%20around%20lengthy%2C%20utterly%20unpronounceable%20words%20that%20no-one%20understands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20despite%20his%20widely%20acknowledged%20talents%2C%20or%20maybe%20because%20of%20them%2C%20Tharoor%20stands%20at%20a%20crossroads%20in%20his%20political%20career%20today%2C%20unsure%20of%20which%20route%20to%20take%20in%20case%20he%20reaches%20a%20dead-end%20with%20no%20way%20to%20get%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ruling%20Trio%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20party's%20ruling%20clique%20in%20his%20home%20state%20of%20Kerala%2C%20the%20trio%20of%20powerful%20AICC%20general%20secretary%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20confidante%20K.C.%20Venugopal%2C%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20V.D.%20Satheeshan%2C%20and%20man%20for%20all%20seasons%20Ramesh%20Chennithala%2C%20is%20unwilling%20to%20cede%20space%20in%20state%20politics%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20national%20level%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20obsession%20with%20caste%20leaves%20little%20room%20for%20English-speaking%20elites%20as%20he%20scouts%20for%20OBCs%2C%20Dalits%20and%20tribals%20to%20craft%20a%20new%20Congress%20of%2C%20for%20and%20by%20the%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20danger%20of%20being%20deemed%20irrelevant%20is%20real%20and%20imminent%20in%20this%20scenario.%20It%20is%20also%20unacceptable%20for%20Tharoor%2C%20who%20has%20grown%20used%20to%20being%20in%20the%20limelight%20after%20a%20meteoric%20rise%20in%20politics%20despite%20being%20an%20outsider.%20He%20quickly%20became%20a%20star%20with%20a%20ministership%20to%20boot%20during%20the%20UPA%20years%20under%20the%20guardianship%20of%20Manmohan%20Singh%20and%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERebellion%20In%20The%20Ranks%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2068%2C%20Tharoor%20seems%20convinced%20he%20has%20enough%20years%20of%20active%20public%20life%20left%20in%20him%20to%20go%20down%20without%20a%20fight.%20He%20fired%20the%20first%20salvo%20with%20crafty%20timing%2C%20boasting%20of%20%26quot%3Boptions'%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20Congress%20had%20no%20use%20for%20his%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20rebellious%20noises%20could%20not%20have%20come%20at%20a%20more%20inopportune%20moment%20for%20the%20party.%20Assembly%20polls%20are%20due%20in%20Kerala%20early%20next%20year.%20It's%20an%20election%20the%20Congress%20not%20only%20hopes%20to%2C%20but%20desperately%20needs%20to%20win%20to%20shake%20off%20the%20'loser'%20tag%20it%20has%20acquired%20after%20a%20string%20of%20defeats%20in%20recent%20state%20ballots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETharoor%20does%20not%20have%20the%20stature%20of%20Congress%20greats%20in%20Kerala%20like%20K.%20Karunakaran%20or%20even%20A.K.%20Antony.%20However%2C%20he%20is%20a%20four-time%20MP%20from%20Thiruvanthapuram%20with%20enough%20of%20a%20national%20profile%20to%20make%20headlines%20every%20time%20he%20opens%20his%20mouth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20can%20hardly%20afford%20dissonance%20in%20its%20ranks%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20a%20crucial%20election.%20Nor%20can%20it%20contend%20with%20restlessness%20in%20its%20parliamentary%20party.%20It%20has%20just%2099%20members%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20a%20number%20it%20reached%20with%20great%20difficulty%20after%20humiliating%20scores%20in%20two%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20already%20facing%20the%20wrath%20of%20its%20INDIA%20partners%20who%20have%20been%20heaping%20contempt%20on%20the%20Congress%20for%20its%20dismal%20performance%20in%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Haryana%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20and%20Jharkhand%20last%20year%20and%20in%20Delhi%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20Congress%20Listening%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETharoor's%20warring%20moves%20had%20their%20impact.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20summoned%20him%20to%20Delhi%20for%20a%20meeting%20that%20Tharoor%20had%20been%20seeking%20for%20months%20but%20was%20denied.%20It%20was%20a%20one-on-one%20meeting%2C%20so%20reports%20are%20sketchy.%20But%20Tharoor%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20placed%20his%20cards%20on%20the%20table%20and%20asked%20for%20a%20more%20meaningful%20role%20in%20the%20party%2C%20either%20in%20Kerala%20or%20in%20Parliament%20or%20in%20the%20AICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20telling%20that%20Tharoor%20has%20not%20been%20allowed%20to%20participate%20in%20any%20major%20debate%20in%20Parliament%2C%20which%20is%20his%20acknowledged%20forte.%20He%20is%20said%20to%20have%20been%20keen%20to%20speak%20in%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20Constitution.%20However%2C%20that%20privilege%20was%20given%20to%20Manish%20Tiwari%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20was%20quite%20noncommittal%20with%20Tharoor%20but%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20latter%20decided%20to%20attend%20the%20scheduled%20meeting%20of%20Kerala%20leaders%20in%20New%20Delhi%20to%20discuss%20future%20strategies%20in%20the%20poll-bound%20state%20is%20an%20indication%20that%20he%20is%20still%20hopeful%20of%20finding%20space%20in%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20LDF-UDF%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Tharoor%20talked%20of%20%26quot%3Boptions''%20in%20the%20podcast%20that%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20he%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20two%20minds%20about%20acting%20on%20them.%20Commmunist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20(CPI-M)%20leader%20Isaac%20Thomas%20has%20said%20that%20Tharoor%20would%20be%20welcome%20in%20the%20ruling%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%20(LDF)%20alliance.%20But%20Tharoor%20would%20only%20be%20a%20small%20fish%20in%20a%20big%20pond%20in%20a%20party%20swarming%20with%20ambitious%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20there%20is%20no%20guarantee%20that%20the%20LDF%20will%20win%20a%20third%20term%20in%20office%20in%20Kerala%20and%20offer%20Tharoor%20a%20ministerial%20berth.%20The%20state%20is%20locked%20in%20revolving%20door%20politics%20with%20the%20CPI(M)-led%20LDF%20and%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Democratic%20Front%20(UDF)%20alternating%20governments%20for%20the%20past%20many%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LDF's%20second%20consecutive%20victory%20in%202020%20was%20a%20complete%20surprise%20and%20came%20on%20the%20back%20of%20a%20split%20in%20the%20UDF%2C%20which%20played%20hard%20ball%20with%20the%20Mani%20faction%20of%20the%20Kerala%20Congress%20and%20virtually%20forced%20an%20important%20ally%20into%20the%20arms%20of%20the%20CPI(M).%20A%20significant%20section%20of%20the%20Christian%20vote%20loyal%20to%20the%20Kerala%20Congress%20deserted%20the%20UDF%20and%20helped%20the%20LDF%20coast%20to%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20May%20Be%20Impractical%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20feelers%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20making%20a%20desperate%20push%20for%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20Kerala.%20However%2C%20most%20observers%20feel%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20before%20it%20can%20hope%20to%20win%20the%20state.%20Inducting%20Tharoor%20into%20the%20BJP%20or%20joining%20hands%20with%20a%20regional%20party%20headed%20by%20him%20can%2C%20at%20best%2C%20eat%20into%20Congress%20votes%20and%20possibly%20help%20the%20LDF%20to%20win%20a%20third%20successive%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20that%20Tharoor%20can%20hope%20for%20in%20this%20situation%20is%20to%20be%20rewarded%20with%20a%20ministerial%20portfolio%20in%20the%20Modi%20government.%20But%20he%20may%20have%20to%20be%20content%20with%20a%20downsized%20profile%20like%20another%20Congress%20renegade%2C%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20who%20has%20all%20but%20vanished%20from%20the%20public%20radar%20except%20when%20the%20BJP%20high%20command%20wants%20to%20enjoy%20the%20spectacle%20of%20an%20erstwhile%20royal%20sparring%20with%20a%20political%20dynast%20(Rahul%20Gandhi).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeighing%20All%20'Options'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETharoor%20craves%20the%20spotlight.%20So%20he%20must%20be%20weighing%20his%20%26quot%3Boptions%26quot%3B%20very%20carefully%2C%20lest%20he%20jumps%20from%20the%20frying%20pan%20into%20the%20fire.%20According%20to%20well-placed%20sources%20who%20have%20some%20inkling%20of%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%20his%20mind%2C%20Tharoor%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20another%20senior%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Kerala%2C%20M.K.%20Raghavan%2C%20who%20apparently%20also%20resents%20the%20trio%20lording%20it%20over%20the%20state%20unit.%20It%20seems%20that%20after%20a%20long%20discussion%2C%20they%20have%20decided%20to%20wait%20and%20watch%20till%20the%20panchayat%20elections%20are%20held%20six%20months%20from%20now.%20Tharoor%20must%20hope%20that%20the%20local%20polls%20will%20indicate%20which%20way%20the%20political%20winds%20are%20blowing%20in%20the%20state%20and%20help%20him%20to%20make%20up%20his%20mind%20about%20his%20future%20course%20of%20action.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20he%20would%20certainly%20not%20want%20to%20go%20the%20way%20of%20Karunakaran%20who%20left%20the%20Congress%20to%20form%20his%20own%20party.%20Despite%20his%20stature%2C%20popularity%20and%20political%20astuteness%2C%20his%20party%20flopped%20and%20Karunakaran%20faded%20into%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740810000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4f5r173g_shashi-tharoor_625x300_24_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-really-are-shashi-tharoors-options-7821584%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Although%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20talked%20of%20%26quot%3Boptions%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20podcast%20that%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20he%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20two%20minds%20about%20acting%20on%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-really-are-shashi-tharoors-options-7821584%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Class%2010%20boy%20succumbs%20to%20injuries%20after%20clash%20between%20students%20in%20Kerala%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740809712000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118643296%2Cimgsize-94326.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkozhikode%2Fclass-10-boy-succumbs-to-injuries-after-clash-between-students-in-kerala%2Farticleshow%2F118643048.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2016-year-old%20student%2C%20Muhammed%20Shahabas%2C%20died%20due%20to%20critical%20head%20injuries%20from%20a%20student%20clash%20near%20a%20tuition%20center%20in%20Kozhikode.%20Five%20students%20have%20been%20detained%20and%20will%20face%20charges%20of%20murder.%20Authorities%20are%20investigating%20the%20incident%2C%20and%20the%20Education%20Minister%20has%20called%20for%20a%20departmental%20review.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkozhikode%2Fclass-10-boy-succumbs-to-injuries-after-clash-between-students-in-kerala%2Farticleshow%2F118643048.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUr