%20our%20hearts%20set%20on%20serving%20biryani%20at%20the%20wedding%2C%20so%20we%20approached%20a%20local%20vendor.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20reluctant%20to%20change%20his%20packaging%2C%20which%20was%20a%20key%20concern%20for%20us.%20After%20some%20thought%2C%20we%20discovered%20sugarcane%20bagasse%20packaging%20and%20considered%20buying%20it%20ourselves%2C%20asking%20the%20vendor%20to%20use%20it%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebiryani%3C%2Fem%3E.%20However%2C%20we%20were%20not%20sure%20if%20he%20would%20allow%20us%20to%20do%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FZero-waste-signage-1_11zon-1740756775-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20made%20sure%20that%20none%20of%20the%20waste%20generated%20at%20their%20wedding%20reached%20the%20landfill%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FZero-waste-signage-1_11zon-1740756775-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FZero-waste-signage-1_11zon-1740756775-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FZero-waste-signage-1_11zon-1740756775-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FZero-waste-signage-1_11zon-1740756775-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FZero-waste-signage-1_11zon-1740756775-900x1200.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FZero-waste-signage-1_11zon-1740756775-600x800.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FZero-waste-signage-1_11zon-1740756775-450x600.jpeg%20450w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2